{506}

Thou therefore endure hardness, as a good soldier of Jesus
Christ.--_II Timothy 2:3_.

Be thou faithful unto death, and I will give thee the crown of
life.--_Revelations 2:10_.

Walk worthily of God, who calleth you unto his kingdom and glory.
--_I Thessalonians 2:12_.

Hold fast the profession of our faith without wavering; for he is
